add table ip ferm
flush table ip ferm
add chain ip ferm INPUT { type filter hook input priority 0; }
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 22 reject with icmp type prot-unreachable
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 23 reject with icmp type net-prohibited
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 24 reject with icmp type host-prohibited
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 25 reject with icmp type net-unreachable
